{"tid":2515514,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"23歲男子被搜出行山杖等 早前蘇文隆指必然意圖損壞公物判監9個月 今向高院上訴 李運騰需時考慮裁決","createTime":"2021-05-04T04:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T05:29:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"054ef3b305d9900c01de68d522f9062f8459f298","tid":2515514,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T04:57:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15418&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGngESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=6d23ae74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15418</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第一庭<br />\n#李運騰法官<br />\n#20200119大埔<br />\n#不服定罪上訴 #不服刑罰上訴 <br />\n<br />\n黃(23) <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n管有適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法用途<br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n被控於2020年1月19日在大埔大元邨中央公園管有兩個鐵錘、一根登山杖、一個點燃器及一把多用途摺刀。<br />\n<br />\n經審訊後定罪，於2020年10月8日被判處9個月監禁，即時申請保釋等候上訴獲批<br />\n<br />\n裁決按此 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9657\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9657&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGngESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=4f1e5138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9657</a>)👈🏿<br />\n判刑按此 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10097&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGngESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=a7971029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10097</a>)👈🏿<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n申請及答辯雙方陳詞完畢，法庭需時考慮<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2021年5月17日1000高等法院宣讀判詞，期間申請人以現有條件保釋。<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛"},{"pid":"9ef77e2160fec87dba79cbc48b7ddf2f1221a353","tid":2515514,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T04:58:05.000Z","msg"